                    {
                      "k": "description",
                      "v": "Weekly Python agent (via GitHub Actions) tracks Chinese AI papers from arXiv & Hugging Face, mapping orgs with OpenAlex ROR. It uses DeepSeek-V4-Flash for summaries, Claude 4.6 Sonnet for validation, and pgvector for Notion deduplication. Papers are scored for impact & conflict-tagged, then published to GitHub Pages & Buttondown."
